# NWN core constraints

- Source of truth is the Nasher tree under `src/` — not `.mod`, `.hak`, or `.tlk` files.
- Never commit build artifacts: `*.mod`, `*.hak`, `*.tlk`, `*.ncs`, `*.erf`.
- Never commit secrets: `.env`, `docker/.env`, `docker/.env.staging`, `docker/.env.prod`.
- Toolchain versions are pinned in `docs/design/toolchain.md` — do not bump without review.
- Propose toolchain changes through normal PR review, not autonomous version bumps.

## Layout

- `src/scripts/` — NWScript source (compiles to git-ignored `.ncs`)
- `src/module/`, `src/areas/`, `src/dialogs/`, `src/blueprints/` — Nasher JSON/GFF
- `build/dist/` — packaged artifacts (git-ignored)
- `database/migrations/` — append-only PostgreSQL schema

## Script naming

| Prefix | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `inc_*` | Utility/library includes |
| `db_*` | Database repository functions |
| `sys_*` | Gameplay systems |
| `evt_*` | Event dispatcher entry points |
| `qst_*` | Quest logic |
| `adm_*` | Admin/DM commands |
| `plc_*` / `cre_*` / `trg_*` | Per-object scripts |
